<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Your LaunchLook report is ready</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0; padding:0; background:#FAF7F2; color:#1F1B16; font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6;">
  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#FAF7F2; padding:24px 0;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table role="presentation" width="560" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="max-width:560px; background:#FFFFFF; border:1px solid #E7E0D6; border-radius:8px; padding:32px 32px 28px;">
          <tr>
            <td>
              <p style="margin:0 0 4px; font-size:11px; font-weight:600; color:#B45309; letter-spacing:0.18em; text-transform:uppercase;">
                LaunchLook
              </p>
              <h1 style="margin:0 0 18px; font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:24px; line-height:1.25; color:#1F1B16; font-weight:500;">
                Your report is ready, {{ customer.first_name }}.
              </h1>

              <p style="margin:0 0 14px; color:#1F1B16;">Hi {{ customer.first_name }},</p>

              <p style="margin:0 0 14px; color:#1F1B16;">
                Here's what your first users will hit on <strong>{{ customer.app_name }}</strong>. The findings are attached as{% if customer.tier in ('Scale Up Package', 'Pro Package') %} four{% else %} three{% endif %} PDFs, sorted by who encounters what first:
              </p>

              <ul style="margin:0 0 18px; padding-left:18px; color:#1F1B16;">
                <li style="margin-bottom:6px;">
                  <strong>Main Report</strong>
                  ({{ n_findings }} finding{{ '' if n_findings == 1 else 's' }}, sorted by severity)
                </li>
                <li style="margin-bottom:6px;">
                  <strong>Quick Start Guide</strong>
                  (a one-page card you can hand to your first users)
                </li>
                {% if customer.tier in ('Scale Up Package', 'Pro Package') %}
                <li style="margin-bottom:6px;">
                  <strong>User Guide</strong>
                  (a 2-3 page doc you can use as onboarding material or share in a help centre)
                </li>
                {% endif %}
                <li>
                  <strong>Pre-Launch Checklist</strong>
                  (a 7-section list to run before sharing your live link)
                </li>
              </ul>

              <p style="margin:0 0 14px; color:#1F1B16;">
                All open in any PDF reader. No login or Notion account needed.
              </p>

              <p style="margin:0 0 14px; color:#1F1B16;">
                Each finding includes a copy-paste fix prompt for {{ customer.builder }}. Start at the top, paste the prompts in, verify the fix on your live URL, and move down the list.
              </p>

              <p style="margin:0 0 18px; color:#1F1B16;">
                If anything in the report isn't clear, or you want a re-scan after fixes, just reply to this email.
              </p>

              <p style="margin:0 0 4px; color:#1F1B16;">Thanks for trying LaunchLook.</p>
              <p style="margin:0; color:#1F1B16;">LaunchLook</p>

              <div style="border-top:1px solid #E7E0D6; border-left:3px solid #B45309; padding:14px 16px; margin-top:24px; background:#F4EFE7; border-radius:4px;">
                <p style="margin:0 0 6px; font-weight:600; color:#1F1B16;">Applied your fixes? Get a Fix Check.</p>
                <p style="margin:0; font-size:13px; color:#1F1B16;">
                  Reply with &ldquo;recheck&rdquo; once you&rsquo;ve worked through the report and we&rsquo;ll re-walk your site for $19 &mdash; or $9 if you book within 14 days of this report. Confirms what&rsquo;s fixed and catches anything new that broke along the way.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div style="border:1px solid #E7E0D6; padding:14px 16px; margin-top:16px; background:#FFFFFF; border-radius:4px;">
                <p style="margin:0 0 4px; font-weight:600; font-size:13px; color:#1F1B16;">Know another founder who&rsquo;s about to launch?</p>
                <p style="margin:0; font-size:13px; color:#6B6359;">
                  Forward this email and mention your name. I&rsquo;ll give you <strong style="color:#1F1B16;">$10 off a future audit</strong> &mdash; no referral codes, just a reply.
                </p>
              </div>

              <hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #E7E0D6; margin:24px 0 16px;" />

              <p style="margin:0; font-size:12px; color:#6B6359;">
                LaunchLook · <a href="https://launchlook.app" style="color:#B45309; text-decoration:none;">launchlook.app</a> · prepared {{ delivered_at }}<br />
                Confidential. Prepared for {{ customer.first_name }} only.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
        <p style="margin:14px 0 0; font-size:11px; color:#6B6359;">
          Sent because you bought a LaunchLook checkup. Reply to this email if you'd like a refund within 7 days.
        </p>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
